<h1>微</h1><p class=neha><span style="color:#990000;">wēi</span><span class=alesi>(wei1)</span> <span class=lesi>// pronunciation of 微 in Mandarin Pinyin</span></p><h2>Basic information about 微</h2><div class=abo>
